transcripts:
[MUSIC PLAYING]

Don't Laugh. This is super serious. I'm in a fragrance add people. Living in fantasy -- a flashbulb filled fragrance fantasy. Because the world of scent isn't about making sense; It's about making sexy faces. It's about running down hallways in slow motion making sexy faces. Searching for an answer only to find more questions like who's this gorgeous guy? and why does he smell so darn good?

Holy nostrils! that smells so nice. Sorry I'm going back in. What is that? 

I know right!

Gain by Gain
